VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT javax\.xml\.parsers\.DocumentBuilderFactory
WHEN EXPR MISSING:setFeature.*XMLConstants\.FEATURE_SECURE_PROCESSING|setFeature.*disallow-doctype-decl|setExpandEntityReferences\s*\(\s*false|XMLInputFactory.*IS_SUPPORTING_EXTERNAL_ENTITIES.*false
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the use of javax.xml.parsers.DocumentBuilderFactory, which may lead to XML external entity (XXE) attacks.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure Package: javax.xml.parsers.DocumentBuilderFactory.
